# TypeScript Constraints

- Always use `pnpm` for package management (`pnpm install`, `pnpm build`).
- Ensure APIs are async-first and strongly typed.
- Never bypass the shared fetch wrapper/API client if one exists.
- Validate using `eslint` and `prettier`.
- Ensure chart rendering strictly expects Vega-Lite specification objects.
